#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Wprowadzenie"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kontact; is the integrated solution for personal information management. "
#| "It combines the well-known &kde; applications for email, scheduling, "
#| "address book, notes, and newsgroups (&kmail;, &korganizer;, "
#| "&kaddressbook;, &knotes;, and &knode;) into a single interface. Being "
#| "based on a true component framework &kontact; provides exactly the same "
#| "functionality as the stand-alone applications, and adds more features, by "
#| "making use of the integrated way &kontact; runs the applications as "
#| "components. Users still retain the choice of which applications are run "
#| "within &kontact; and which are run stand-alone."
msgid ""
"&kontact; is the integrated solution for personal information management. It "
"combines the well-known &kde; applications for email, scheduling and address "
"book (&kmail;, &korganizer;, &kaddressbook;) into a single interface. Being "
"based on a true component framework &kontact; provides exactly the same "
"functionality as the stand-alone applications, and adds more features, by "
"making use of the integrated way &kontact; runs the applications as "
"components. Users still retain the choice of which applications are run "
"within &kontact; and which are run stand-alone."
msgstr ""
"&kontact; jest zintegrowanym rozwiązaniem do zarządzania osobistymi "
"informacjami (&PIM;). Łączy w sobie dobrze znane programy &kde; do wysyłania "
"poczty, terminarz, książkę adresową, notatnik i grupy dyskusyjne (&kmail-"
"mianownik;, &korganizer-mianownik; &kaddressbook; &knotes; i &knode;) w "
"jednym prostym interfejsie. &kontact;, będąc opartym na wielu komponentach, "
"zapewnia dokładnie taką samą funkcjonalność jak każdy z nich oddzielnie, a "
"także dodaje nowe funkcje. Użytkownicy w dalszym ciągu mają wybór, który "
"program uruchomić w ramach programu &kontact;, a który oddzielnie."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "In addition to the functionality of the individual applications &kontact; "
#| "provides, a summary view and advanced drag &amp; drop features between "
#| "components."
msgid ""
"In addition to the functionality of the individual applications, &kontact; "
"provides a summary view and advanced drag &amp; drop features between "
"components."
msgstr ""
"W uzupełnieniu możliwości każdego z programów, &kontact; jest wyposażony w "
"widok podsumowania oraz zaawansowane funkcje przeciągnij i upuść pomiędzy "
"poszczególnymi komponentami."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kontact; Components"
msgstr "Komponenty programu &kontact;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kontact; integrates the following applications. See the individual "
"application manuals for details on how to use them. These apply to running "
"them as components inside &kontact; just as well as running them stand-alone."
msgstr ""
"&kontact; łączy poniższe programy. Zobacz ich podręczniki, aby nauczyć się "
"je obsługiwać. Odnosi się to do pracy komponentów w ramach programu "
"&kontact; jak i do uruchomionych oddzielnie."

