#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:679
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <quote>To-do List</quote> plugin for &kontact;'s Summary View adds an "
#| "area in the view labeled <guilabel>To-dos</guilabel>. This area contains "
#| "all current to-dos, including ones that have been completed. It displays "
#| "the title of the to-do, the percentage of completion, and the current "
#| "status of the to-do. Note that you can purge all completed to-dos via the "
